"name":"What is CompTIA Security+ Certification?",
"acceptedAnswer":{
"@type":"Answer",
"text":"CompTIA Security+ is a globally recognized cybersecurity certification that validates foundational knowledge in security operations, threats, vulnerabilities, governance, risk management and cloud security."
